{{Quote|Come closer and I'll shove that stick up your bunghole and fuck you bloody!|Rorge to [[Arya Stark]]|The Night Lands}}

'''Rorge''' is a recurring character in the [[Season 1|first]], [[Season 2|second]] and [[Season 4|fourth]] seasons. He is played by guest star [[Andy Beckwith]] and debuts in the &quot;[[The Night Lands]],&quot; though he was also portrayed by an unidentified extra in &quot;[[Fire and Blood]]&quot;. Rorge is a criminal, forcibly recruited into the [[Night's Watch]].

